{"tid":2199371,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"胡志偉料民調結果解決大部分矛盾　已問心無愧","createTime":"2020-09-12T06:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T07:00:39.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43296520435330d40cf25482a9a7a8a448999102","tid":2199371,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n15名民主派議員將透過香港民研本月21日起做的民調結果，決定留任或杯葛議會。民主黨主席胡志偉預料，無論民主派作出任何決定都會受到批評，但他已努力減少分歧，過程中問心無愧。<br />\n提出以「民調定去留」的胡志偉接受專訪時說，民主派內部如果因策略分歧而出現矛盾，不利現時的抗爭運動。為了民主派團結，他希望透過民調機制減少爭議，並將去或留的理據解釋給市民知道，同時期望建立一個機制，如果將來遇到政治爭議，都可透過民調處理。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549208-20200912.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549208-20200912.htm&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=e2ab1a20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549208-20200912.htm&h=cd673e65\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549208-20200912.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：延任與現屆議會本質無分別 民意授權無變動<br />\n...<br />\n鄭松泰說，他會接受延任安排，但仍要視乎泛民主派的討論。若公眾認為選舉制度已無意思及無認受性，從此不再參選選舉，他會持開放態度處理。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543446-20200813.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543446-20200813.htm&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=07732962\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543446-20200813.htm&h=6e4ad178\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543446-20200813.htm</a>"},{"pid":"56a711e09a72f8aeb8a2d55e1bb2a663e284e521","tid":2199371,"uid":269061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"熱9 用偽學術字眼去包裝自己貪財怕死跟緊民主黨。淪落"}]}